.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, blues, metal, house
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the fan of house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the fan of house is on the far right##1
4. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the fan of metal is between the fan of soul and the fan of blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | metal           | soul | house  |
| Sport         | badminton | weightlifting | soccer   | lacrosse |

