.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, trance, indie, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, train, tram
1. the fan of trance is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the fan of reggae is between the person driving the bike and the fan of indie##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | trance | reggae | indie      |
| Transport     | train | bike    | taxi  | tram |

