2. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the car##2
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | rowing | climbing | cricket     | surfing   |
| Transport   | car   | trike     | boat | subway |

