.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, blueberry, pear, asparagus
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, handball, basketball
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person eating pear##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person eating blueberry and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | asparagus   | pear      | blueberry   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | basketball | skateboarding | handball | parkour |

