2. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating corn and the person eating nectarine##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
