.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, puzzles, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, soul, dubstep
1. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of house is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of house is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | traveling | puzzles | hiking | card-games |
| Music-Genre   | soul          | hip-hop     | dubstep  | house     |

