1. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the polish is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the turtle and the dutch##2
4. the owner of the snake is the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | polish | dutch | malaysian | french |
| Pet           | ferret  | snake  | guinea-pig | turtle      |

