1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the indian is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the egyptian and the dutch##2
5. the dutch is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | indian   | egyptian   | malaysian | dutch |
| Sport         | rugby | biathlon | weightlifting     | handball    |

