.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, reading, puzzles, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, horse, dog
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | rock-climbing     | chess | reading |
| Pet     | rabbit | dog | horse       | hamster     |

 